  <td class="infotd">
    <h3>Bootcamp 2021: Hit Your friendly fly</h3>
    <p>
	My first programming project, concluding the 2 week Programming Bootcamp at 
	City (2021). This Processing project demonstrays good understanding of variables, if functions, noice function and usage of mouse.  I created 2d game where player controls
a slipper and suppose to hit a fly. In the game I implemented detection of wheather slipper hit a fly or not, used random to determine movement of fly, 
created title screen, score counter and many other things. Big challenge for me was creation of animation form slipper when it hits the table and debugging game
(restricting abuse of button mashing and so on). 
    </p>

